This is/will be my Reddit Game Jam #6 entry.

Expect really, really ugly code.

I'll be using my own engine ("Oryx Engine"), which is GPL'd
and has been up on my github for a while. I'll be using Ogre3d,
OpenAL, bullet, Chaiscript and OIS through the engine.

